{"tid":6650,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［復古運動］週日小丑神崇拜","createTime":"2016-11-27T12:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-27T14:48:30.000Z","uid":23701,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"73f31beb0f1f65895da03adb0dfa576f40e3ae90","tid":6650,"uid":23701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-27T12:58:19.000Z","msg":"我們在連加的神，<br />\n願人都尊神的名為膠；<br />\n願神的國降臨；<br />\n願神的旨意行在地上，<br />\n如同行在連加。<br />\n我們日常用的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求神今日賜給我們。<br />\n又求饒恕我們的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為我們饒恕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 的人。<br />\n不叫我們遇見試探，<br />\n拯救我們脫離高登。<br />\n因為國度、權柄、榮耀、<br />\n全是神的，直到永遠。<br />\n膠們。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">復興小丑教 你我有責</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連加Hkg+ 千秋萬世</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"